^-{    POSTPONING THE TRUMP LEAD FOR A SPECIFIC DISCARD    }
^-|cp||FP||AT|^B@2^Y@3You cannot simply make up your mind that you need to discard a loser, and then discard any small card at all. Very often it makes a vast difference if you discard, say, a diamond instead of a club when you have a choice. Consider, for example, the following deal:|
