pn|You,,,|st||SK|S|md|1SKJT72HA62DA7CA92,S54HQJT4D652CKJ83,SQ983H753DKQ94C76,SA6HK98DJT83CQT54|RH||AH|Board 3|mb|4sppp|pc|hQ|NT|^B@2
